{
  "stem": "23155.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I must tell you, they were shooting left and right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The Germans had their turnips and potatoes, you know, like in storage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were like mounds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So the girls would go and dig them up so to have something to eat, because nobody-- nobody gave us anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- and these Hungarians just would go and just would shoot them because they were digging those rutabagas.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Anyway, nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Everybody left us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't know how it was that somebody said that the Red Cross is coming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I-- I can't remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So there were about four or five of us, said, we have to prepare for the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We took a table-- found a table somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We went walking with a table on the-- there was no-- no soldiers, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Everybody left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There were some SS women who were with us, and one of them was called Bubbie.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And Bubbie came and said she wants that we should hide her, because she knows something is going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we said, of course, no way, Bubbie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Bubbie, go where you came from.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "That wasn't her real name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We called her Bubbie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And so we were walking with this table to the entrance of the camp, and there at once there was this huge tank with a white star on it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the turret opened, and a young man with curly hair appeared and he said, a division of the Allies is coming to liberate you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And in the meantime, some Germans must have been hiding because they started shooting at us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the girl next to me, her name was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Herzog, ?] she had a-- a shoulder pad, and one of the bullets lodged in her shoulder pad.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
